{\section*{saMsakxqqtAyoVgada parxshenxgaLige utatxrisabeVkAda parxkaraNa.}}\label{page19}

(saMsakxqqta BASeya vAyxsaMgavananxBivaqdidhxpaDisalu, hiMdomemx saMsakxqqtAyoVgavoMdu keVMdarx sakAR\-radiMda rUpugoMDu, aneVka vidAyxsaMsethxgaLige aBipArxya saMgarxhakAkxgi (AyoVgavu) parxshAnxvaLiyanunx kaLuhisi yoVgayx utatxragaLanunx bayasitutx. A samayadalilx naMjanagUDu tAlUlxku heDatale keSxVtarxdalilx asATxMgayoVgavijAcnxnamaMdirada keVMdarx kAyARlayavu tananx kAyaRgaLanunx naDesutitxtutx. vijAcnxna\-maMdirakUkx  parxshAnxvaLiyu baMdidadxriMda maMdirAdhayxkaSxrAda shirxV shirxVraMga mahAguruvu anugarxhisida viSayagaLanunx (saMsakxqqtiVkarisi) meVlakxMDa AyoVgakekx kaLuhisalAgitutx. adanunx ililx muMdiDalAgide. {\rm 13-02-1956})  

