{\section*{saMsakxqqtAdhayxyanadalilx ASaRsaMparxdAyada anavxya-saMjiVviniV}}\label{page45}

\begin{itemize}
\item[17-si] shasatxrXgaLa adhayxyanavanUnx adhAyxpanavanUnx, matetx saMjiVviniya mUlaka viVrayxvatatxravAgi mADi,
