\end{shloka}
\end{itemize}

(atayxMta sUkaSxmXdashiRyAda kwtasxneV! maMtarxsasxSapxqqgaLAdaMtaha QuSigaLige muMdALAda ninanx gu\-ruvu kushaliyAgiruvanaSeTx? loVkavu uSaNxkiraNanAda sUrayayxna deseyiMda parxboVdhavanunx-kAyaR\-paTutavxkekx beVkAda shakitxyanunx paDedukoLuLxvaMte, niVnu yAva QuSiyiMda saMsatxvAda jAcnxnAginxyanunx (atamx parxboVdhakoDuva shakitxyanunx) paDedukoMDeyoV A QuSiyu kushali tAneV?)

\begin{itemize}
\begin{shloka}
\item[2.] `kAyeVna vAcA manasA\char'263 pi shashavxtf yatasxMBaqtaM vASavadheyyaRloVpi|\\\label{56}
