\item[3.] `AdhAra baMdha parxmuKeYH parxyatenxYH saMvadhiRtAnAM sutaniviRsheVSamf |\\\label{page56}
kacicxnanx vAyAvxdirupapalxvoV vaH sharxmaciCxdAmasharxmapAdapAnAmf||'
